    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1863-11-16T23:59:59-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1863-11-16T00:00:00-05:00" n="457"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d457">
                <head>
                    <persName type="from">Mr. Pruyn</persName> to <persName type="to">Mr.
                        Seward</persName>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#left">No. 75.]</seg>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Legation of the United States in Japan</hi>, <hi
                                rend="italic">Kanagawa, Yokohama</hi>,</placeName>
                        <date calendar="gregorian" when="1863-11-16">
                            <hi rend="italic">November</hi> 16, 1863.</date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>
                    <hi rend="smallcaps">Sir</hi>: I have the honor to inform you that the prince of
                    Satsuma has agreed to pay, within four days, the sum of <hi rend="italic"
                    >£</hi>25,000 demanded by the government of Great Britain as a further indemnity
                    for the murder of Mr. Richardson in September, 1862.</p>
                <p>The demand for the surrender of the murderers has been practically abandoned,
                    though the prince has promised to use his efforts for their discovery and
                    arrest.</p>
                <p>I have the honor to be, sir, very respectfully, your most obedient servant,</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>ROBERT H. PRUYN, <hi rend="italic">Minister Resident in Japan.</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
                <postscript>
                    <p>Hon. <hi rend="smallcaps">William H. Seward</hi>, <hi rend="italic">&amp;c.,
                            &amp;c., &amp;c.</hi>
                    </p>
                </postscript>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
